title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - Klay Thompson takes down the Lakers and solving the Westbrook problem
itunes:title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - Klay Thompson takes down the Lakers and solving the Westbrook problem
description:
Jason breaks down what the Lakers showed in a tight loss to the Warriors, highlights the difficult conversation the team needs to have with Russell Westbrook and reveals who they need to target on the buyout market.
